{"tid":2494980,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底情侶之間互相同大家講自己喺邊係咪正常？","createTime":"2021-04-19T02:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T03:00:26.000Z","uid":253369,"like":24,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"413e2ce1652130ed394a76b7fdf23e9ca611a63a","tid":2494980,"uid":253369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:12:26.000Z","msg":"我都估唔到自己會po感情問題上連燈問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直做緊cd rom<br />\n但我真係想知係咪我要求太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知大家平時係點<br />\n<br />\n最近同女朋友嘈交<br />\n因為成日唔知佢喺邊度<br />\nSignal又好幾個鐘都唔覆我一次<br />\n我話我都知佢可能好忙<br />\n我只係想佢要去邊度用幾秒講聲我知<br />\n<br />\n例如出門口坐巴士 返到公司咪同我講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢就可以專心做嘢<br />\n我又唔使心掛掛<br />\n起碼等我知道佢安全到步<br />\n同佢傾過幾次<br />\n有時好似得過且過咁應承咗我<br />\n但第過兩日又打回原型<br />\n仲話我逼佢交功課...<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家到底互相話大家知喺邊係咪正常要求？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正常<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔正常<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44e41a0661d4eef9e7b0bc318108d2e4046450a","tid":2494980,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"講自己係邊好正常呀"},{"pid":"faec172fb92f3e810dd665dcc3cf58b3a3290ddc","tid":2494980,"uid":37487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:14:18.000Z","msg":"好過你乜都唔講<br />\n分手果陣就砌你生豬肉先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23b267ac7a154f06c86ba877e1e66bb844ebe28","tid":2494980,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"正常呀<br />\n<br />\n利申 a0"},{"pid":"0c1fb5fe7151c0afa1d91c27aaaabb9e3ccbe4e5","tid":2494980,"uid":56912,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:15:24.000Z","msg":"約左